Revision from %revision-date of %title has been deleted.
The Media Revisions UI module adds a Revisions tab for Media entities, where revisions can be reverted or deleted.
The Media Revisions UI module enables you to revert to older versions of media or delete a revision using the Revisions tab.
The Media Revisions UI module uses the Media permissions, which can be set by role on the permissions page.
To delete a revision, you also need permission to delete the media item.
To revert a revision, you also need permission to update the media item.
To view a revision, you also need permission to view the media item.
